A_284 - Sometimes it may happen that you need privacy or mental stability that is a little more robust than what you have in classic circumstances. There is a method to obtain it (for a limited time) which consists in punching the wall without letting anyone know. The pain in the bones that is created and remains &ldquo;secret&rdquo; also helps us to have mental stability and greater privacy, even if it forces us to endure a little pain.